headline.main: UK Zoo Gets License Rejected After Hundreds of Animal Deaths
headline.print_headline: UK Zoo Gets License Rejected After Hundreds of Animal Deaths

lead_paragraph: Local officials in Britain have refused to renew the license of a zoo where nearly 500 animals have died in the last four years.
